                <p><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/games/hollow-knight-silksong/" data-ref-id="5000-493311">Hollow Knight: Silksong</a> is finally here. After what feels like an eternity, Team Cherry's follow-up to the hugely successful 2017 original has been released, and with it comes a <a href="https://www.twitch.tv/drops/campaigns?dropID=28af0e9e-8905-11f0-b499-3a137f91499c" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Twitch Drops campaign</a> for a global badge.</p><p>Unlike emotes, Twitch badges can be customized to appear next to your username when talking in streamers' Twitch chats. The last Twitch badge to be made available in direct conjunction with a game's release was Elden Ring Nightreign's Wylder, which was unlocked by clipping moments from streamers playing the game.</p>



    
